title: Way of the Dogg 1.0[Android][Nan1977]
description:
Way of the Dogg 1.0[Android][Nan1977]



Release Date: July 4, 2013
Genre: Fighting
Developer: 505 Games Srl
Format:. Apk, cache
Version: 1.0
Language: English

System requirements:
==========================

OS Version: Android 2.3 +; Processor Type: ARMv7



In the Way of the Dogg main character will avenge the murder of his girlfriend a bunch of different reptiles. Will help him in this battle style "The Way Dog", which the protagonist has trained himself Snoop Dogg.

Setting:
==========================

1) Copy com.and_505games.WOTDogg folder to sdcard / Android / obb

2) Install APK

3) Play!
